snippet.title: Duke Nukem Forever Enhanced - Version 1.5 release trailer
snippet.description:
The (true) king is back:

Version 1.5 of Duke Nukem Forever Enhanced is now out, with two major improvements in this new release. The Duke Nukem model featured in Triptych's 2009 trailer has been restored and it's now back to action, and as a sneak peek on what will come in the future, I've also tweaked the infamous "The Hive" chapter with new music and fixed writing.

What are you waiting for, Christmas? Download it now:

https://www.moddb.com/mods/duke-nukem-forever-enhanced

https://www.nexusmods.com/dukenukemforever/mods/6

Grabbag cover by Captain_Meatshield:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VJc1IrBJopg
